be the most beautiful structure

00:17:53.440 --> 00:17:55.090 align:middle line:10%
in mathematics.

00:17:55.090 --> 00:17:57.490 align:middle line:84%
It's a fantastic
prospect that this object

00:17:57.490 --> 00:17:59.727 align:middle line:84%
of great mathematical
beauty could describe

00:17:59.727 --> 00:18:01.810 align:middle line:84%
the truth of particle
interactions at the smallest

00:18:01.810 --> 00:18:03.160 align:middle line:90%
scales imaginable.

