00:21:00.260 --> 00:21:02.180 align:middle line:84%
And then from that
excited state it

00:21:02.180 --> 00:21:04.700 align:middle line:84%
expanded into all
possible interactions

00:21:04.700 --> 00:21:07.520 align:middle line:84%
of all these existing particles
and all new particles that

00:21:07.520 --> 00:21:12.140 align:middle line:84%
could pop into existence so
that all universes are happening

00:21:12.140 --> 00:21:13.814 align:middle line:90%
quantum mechanically.

00:21:13.814 --> 00:21:15.230 align:middle line:84%
And we find ourselves
in this one.

00:21:15.230 --> 00:21:17.406 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Why is
