multicellular organisms.

00:25:21.840 --> 00:25:26.760 align:middle line:84%
And you're talking
about trillions

00:25:26.760 --> 00:25:28.525 align:middle line:90%
of interacting things.

00:25:28.525 --> 00:25:30.150 align:middle line:84%
And those interacting
things themselves

00:25:30.150 --> 00:25:31.410 align:middle line:90%
