00:25:31.410 --> 00:25:32.993 align:middle line:84%
A cell doesn't think
about what you're

00:25:32.993 --> 00:25:34.300 align:middle line:90%
going to have for breakfast.

00:25:34.300 --> 00:25:37.200 align:middle line:10%
A cell's just thinking about its
neighbors and what's going on.

00:25:37.200 --> 00:25:39.290 align:middle line:10%
But you put trillions
of things together

00:25:39.290 --> 00:25:41.790 align:middle line:10%
and these trillions of cells
are thinking about what they're

00:25:41.790 --> 00:25:44.770 align:middle line:10%
going to have for breakfast.

00:25:44.770 --> 00:25:45.580 align:middle line:90%
This emerges.

00:25:45.580 --> 00:25:50.170 align:middle line:84%
So when you have vast numbers
of simple interacting things

00:25:50.170 --> 00:25:52.750 align:middle line:84%
but they're interacting in
ways that lead to complexity,

00:25:52.750 --> 00:25:54.790 align:middle line:84%
then we have the emergence
