>>LISI: Who want it, yes.

00:39:44.690 --> 00:39:46.840 align:middle line:84%
And the transactions
happen purely

00:39:46.840 --> 00:39:49.850 align:middle line:84%
in terms of new records
entering the ledger.

00:39:49.850 --> 00:39:51.940 align:middle line:84%
So when I send
